lead_paragraph: Devin Booker had 27 points and nine assists, Alex Len added 19 points and 16 rebounds, and the Phoenix Suns beat the Memphis Grizzlies 109-100 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Booker, Len Lead Suns Past Grizzlies, 109-100
